{"tid":975721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工作壓力爆煲　南亞漢紅磡墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-01-10T01:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T12:44:10.000Z","uid":157545,"like":208,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"a29639d9c4eb8a167fbda2cabbf527e77dc1d837","tid":975721,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190110/photo/bkn-20190110045542058-0110_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190110081646\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190110%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190110045542058-0110_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190110081646&h=6b71adeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日(10日)凌晨4時許，身穿睡褲的南亞漢ANOOP(33歲)，被途人發現昏迷倒臥在紅磡必嘉街與湖光街交界路中，懷疑他從高處墮下，於是報警。救護員到場證實事主當場死亡，警員用帳蓬遮蓋屍體，並封鎖現場調查。受事件影響，現場需封閉一條行車線。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，死者與妻子同住在湖光街7號鴻運閣一單位，近日疑受工作壓力困擾，事發前曾與妻子吵架，隨後走到大廈天台一躍而下。 <br />\n<br />\n警方現場並無檢獲遺書，案件無可疑。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626"},{"pid":"4a087b404aa56bd60af06bbfd43bb0c83b0c4699","tid":975721,"uid":21028,"like":202,"dislike":13,"score":189,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:16:35.000Z","msg":"好大壓力咩 唔啱咪返鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7289b8c6396c2c6c192c9fed3015d53c424d50cf","tid":975721,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b80193ac85df08e74ef07c38cc4c17c60b3ee4","tid":975721,"uid":38030,"like":144,"dislike":15,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"靠打劫過活都唔係咁易，又驚隨時俾人拉"},{"pid":"b1d845ae01c39e0995afc7ecf2389640ee3852cd","tid":975721,"uid":59283,"like":119,"dislike":5,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:01:26.000Z","m